            You retain full ownership of all production data, part definitions, work orders, and other content
            you enter into Vectrik. We do not claim any intellectual property rights over your data. You may
            export your data at any time.
        </p>

        <h3 class="pub-legal-heading">Service Level Agreement</h3>
        <p class="pub-about-text">
            We commit to 99.9% uptime for all paid plans, measured monthly. Scheduled maintenance windows are
            communicated at least 48 hours in advance and are excluded from SLA calculations. Credits are issued
            for SLA breaches upon request.
        </p>

        <h3 class="pub-legal-heading">Acceptable Use</h3>
        <p class="pub-about-text">
            You agree to use Vectrik only for lawful manufacturing management purposes. You may not attempt to
            reverse engineer the platform, interfere with its operation, or use it to store data unrelated to
            your manufacturing operations.
        </p>

        <h3 class="pub-legal-heading">Billing &amp; Cancellation</h3>
        <p class="pub-about-text">
            Subscriptions are billed monthly or annually as selected. You may cancel at any time; access continues
            through the end of the current billing period. We provide 30 days notice before any price changes.
        </p>

        <h3 class="pub-legal-heading">Contact</h3>
        <p class="pub-about-text">
            For questions about these terms, contact us at legal&commat;vectrik.com.
        </p>
